eventDescription: Arunachal Pradesh itself is a jewel in crown of Indian subcontinent. Nature is still undisturbed and well preserved by tradition and culture.We are conducting one bird watching plus nature watch expedition in Namdafa area with association with local NGO Society for Education and Environment Development.

Pench tiger reserve Cillari Gate, Maharashtra Recently I was in Pench Tiger Reserve for bird survey. I have not seen a tiger physically but experienced it every inch I travelled. Pug marks, marking on trees, remaining of tiger kill, alarm calls by Sambar, Langur. Thus I saw tiger every day and every time.Our theme is if tiger is not sighted (people say it is sheer luck) then what. Then every other thing we can experience. Jungle reading with local tribe man, birding, and everything we come across on trail.

Arunachal Pradesh itself is a jewel in crown of Indian subcontinent. Nature is still undisturbed and well preserved by tradition and culture. We are conducting one bird watching plus nature watch expedition in Namdafa Development.
